{"tid":1840274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家係咪嫌未死夠香港人？","createTime":"2020-01-24T18:45:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T18:59:46.000Z","uid":249924,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0fe6a8a1d2baacf77a561b5a8e0ecc501a5aa552","tid":1840274,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:45:06.000Z","msg":"連袁國勇都話未來幾日再唔封關就玩撚完 大家如果睇左武漢d片都知入面幾恐怖 我睇完真係訓唔到 再唔封關就係香港大爆發 然後變武漢 到時死得人多 <br />\n<br />\n政府唔做嘢唯有自己做 自己香港自己救 我地係想攬抄但唔係要死哂d真香港人 <br />\n<br />\n各位我地真係得返最後幾日做野 快d推行動post <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[封印高鐵] 高鐵不封 ! 港人必亡 ! 封印高鐵 !  香港封關 !<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1840241\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1840241</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">自己香港自己救<br />\n<br />\n封關係刻不容緩</span></strong>"},{"pid":"8a6b34f0193b448992a10be8a725e9ccee5ad976","tid":1840274,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:45:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5627c3af989fe1f19f6659b2084b468b300d0203","tid":1840274,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:45:53.000Z","msg":"大家幫推行動post <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"></span>"},{"pid":"194fee39943bc752fe9ae411d676fdaa17cf76e2","tid":1840274,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:46:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b214a18bbc21d36923b4f35967312bde1d6c775e","tid":1840274,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:46:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自己香港自己救</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8256070370faf5f5b71a07b66933f4e154d9db62","tid":1840274,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:46:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />罷工救港 功德無量<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2584ce45eca3b130c9e2366118029a394df424c","tid":1840274,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:46:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ecb4649bf5ffe15d05efeead48152a4592c3de44","tid":1840274,"uid":318928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:47:04.000Z","msg":"要快！必須要有612咁大型  已經冇退路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1840260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1840260</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7bd98b6f63774bb3ad02ac7ac27845f12be7c8be","tid":1840274,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:47:33.000Z","msg":"致四大醫護專業工會<br />\n<br />\n近日致命武漢肺炎肆虐全球，世界各地的政府均已實行嚴謹的防疫措施。唯獨香港特區政府對關口的防疫工作置之不理，令大量懷疑感染新型冠狀病毒的外來患者湧入香港。<br />\n<br />\n港府在防疫工作上力度不足，以及後知後覺的態度，直接令醫護界工作壓力及感染機會大增，甚至需要以抽生死籤來決定進入隔離病房的醫護名單。在未有任何確切治療的方案下，此致命的疫症絕大機會令2003 年沙士事件中，醫護人員因受感染而死亡的傷痛事件重現，再次勾起港人的悲痛回憶。<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，一眾熱心的市民已於2020年1月24日零晨，在《香港地投票》應用程式內發起了一項投票事項。投票只開放予香港境內市民，亦以一系列的措施盡力達至一人一票，其內容如下：<br />\n<br />\n議題：支唔支持醫護大罷工<br />\n投票開放時間：一個月<br />\n截至2020年1月25日零晨為止，24小時內已有1117名香港市民投票，當中約97%支持香港醫護人員罷工，約2%反對及2張廢票。<br />\n<br />\n《香港地投票》應用程式作為一個投票平台，致力為不同民生或政制議題及各種工業行動提供民意基礎。現來信各醫護工會團體，藉此轉達市民的意見。考慮到醫護人員有其專業，亦關乎病人及其家屬的權益。醫護人員罷工與否的決定將完全留待醫護界自行決定，此函只供各大機構作民意參考之用。<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票<br />\n謹啟<br />\n2020-01-25<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.org%2FLetter%2F20200125.pdf&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT2ipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=c007d241\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkvote.org/Letter/20200125.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n有勞大家幫我forword 俾醫護工會同各醫護知<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"706cdb1803f629bc68967a3e649e21dbbe10affc","tid":1840274,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:47:36.000Z","msg":"求下大家推下個行動post"},{"pid":"5aad8630abdd7ff007c5c53808aa176dca1d1dd6","tid":1840274,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:48:07.000Z","msg":"要快！必須要有612咁大型  已經冇退路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1840260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1840260</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"36960082f4e265288a3cf0cbc709c2cb74c4143d","tid":1840274,"uid":271894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:48:19.000Z","msg":"港共唔封 就全港市民去封"},{"pid":"d4e10297092b2270196449e75ac880297c825b7b","tid":1840274,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:49:40.000Z","msg":"[封印高鐵] 高鐵不封 ! 港人必亡 ! 封印高鐵 !  香港封關 !<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1840241\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1840241</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4e8dc0a07c721c42a975d4488bfd193aeadf0160","tid":1840274,"uid":121985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:49:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed5ae7de131750170591aae37115aff247c5d8f0","tid":1840274,"uid":169497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:49:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>全民罷工</strong></span></span><br />\n[red]<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">封關救港[</span></strong>/red]<br />\n<br />\n唔想死就唔好返工<br />\n返工真係高危活動"},{"pid":"a7d1e11add69b26153d7febdfa62df1080ff6b3a","tid":1840274,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T18:50:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>醒下啦香港人 政府唔會救我哋 只能自救</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"f47202b4f9efc2029ca4a9c3435adaf98b52a2a5","ti